FORMAT: 1A

# Nexio IMDb Internal API

Internal, non-commercial IMDb dataset API and portal for Nexio.

# Group Platform

## Health Check [/healthz]

### Get Health [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes

            {
              "status": "ok"
            }

## Readiness Check [/readyz]

### Get Readiness [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes

            {
              "status": "ready"
            }

## Snapshot Metadata [/v1/meta/snapshots]

### List Snapshots [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Snapshot])

## Dataset Stats [/v1/meta/stats]

### Get Stats [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (PlatformStats)

# Group Titles

## Title Detail [/v1/titles/{tconst}]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Title [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TitleDetail)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Attributes (ErrorEnvelope)

## Title Resolve [/v1/titles/resolve{?title,titleType,year}]

### Resolve Title [GET]

+ Parameters
    + title: `Paradise` (string, required)
    + titleType: `tvSeries` (string, optional)
    + year: `2025` (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (ResolvedTitleResponse)

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Attributes (ErrorEnvelope)

## Title Search [/v1/titles/search{?q,titleType,year,includeAkas}]

### Search Titles [GET]

+ Parameters
    + q: `Paradise` (string, required)
    + titleType: `tvSeries` (string, optional)
    + year: `2025` (number, optional)
    + includeAkas: `true` (boolean, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TitleSearchResponse)

## Title Bulk Get [/v1/titles/bulk/get]

### Bulk Get Titles [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkLookupRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkTitleResponse)

## Title Bulk Resolve [/v1/titles/bulk/resolve]

### Bulk Resolve Titles [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkResolveRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkResolvedTitleResponse)

## Title Credits [/v1/titles/{tconst}/credits]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Credits [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CreditsResponse)

## Title Principals [/v1/titles/{tconst}/principals]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Principals [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (PrincipalsResponse)

## Title Crew [/v1/titles/{tconst}/crew]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Crew [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CrewResponse)

## Title Alternate Titles [/v1/titles/{tconst}/akas]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Alternate Titles [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (AkasResponse)

# Group Ratings

## Title Rating [/v1/ratings/{tconst}]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt32459853` (string, required)

### Get Rating [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Rating)

## Ratings Bulk [/v1/ratings/bulk]

### Bulk Get Ratings [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkLookupRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkRatingsResponse)

# Group Series

## Series Episodes [/v1/series/{tconst}/episodes]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Episodes [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (SeriesEpisodesResponse)

## Series Episode Ratings [/v1/series/{tconst}/episode-ratings]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt27444205` (string, required)

### Get Episode Ratings [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (SeriesEpisodeRatingsResponse)

## Resolve Series Episode Ratings [/v1/series/resolve/episode-ratings{?title,titleType,year}]

### Resolve Series Episode Ratings [GET]

+ Parameters
    + title: `Paradise` (string, required)
    + titleType: `tvSeries` (string, optional)
    + year: `2025` (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (SeriesEpisodeRatingsResponse)

## Series Episode Ratings Bulk [/v1/series/bulk/episode-ratings]

### Bulk Get Series Episode Ratings [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkLookupRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkSeriesEpisodeRatingsResponse)

## Episode Detail [/v1/episodes/{tconst}]

+ Parameters
    + tconst: `tt32459853` (string, required)

### Get Episode [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (EpisodeDetail)

## Episode Bulk [/v1/episodes/bulk]

### Bulk Get Episodes [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkLookupRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkEpisodeResponse)

# Group Names

## Name Detail [/v1/names/{nconst}]

+ Parameters
    + nconst: `nm1250791` (string, required)

### Get Name [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (NameDetail)

## Name Search [/v1/names/search{?q}]

### Search Names [GET]

+ Parameters
    + q: `Sterling K. Brown` (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (NameSearchResponse)

## Name Titles [/v1/names/{nconst}/titles]

+ Parameters
    + nconst: `nm1250791` (string, required)

### Get Titles For Name [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (NameTitlesResponse)

## Names Bulk [/v1/names/bulk]

### Bulk Get Names [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkNamesRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkNamesResponse)

# Group Alternate Titles

## Alternate Title Search [/v1/akas/search{?title,region,language}]

### Search Alternate Titles [GET]

+ Parameters
    + title: `Paradies` (string, required)
    + region: `DE` (string, optional)
    + language: `de` (string, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (AkaSearchResponse)

# Group Bulk Jobs

## Bulk Jobs [/v1/bulk/jobs]

### Create Bulk Job [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkJobCreateRequest)

+ Response 202 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkJob)

## Bulk Job [/v1/bulk/jobs/{jobId}]

+ Parameters
    + jobId: `01HZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ` (string, required)

### Get Bulk Job [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkJob)

## Bulk Job Result [/v1/bulk/jobs/{jobId}/result]

+ Parameters
    + jobId: `01HZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ` (string, required)

### Download Bulk Job Result [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (BulkJobResultEnvelope)

# Group Portal Auth

## Start Google Login [/auth/google]

### Redirect To Google [GET]

+ Response 302

## OAuth Callback [/auth/callback]

### Complete Google Login [GET]

+ Response 302

+ Response 401 (application/json)
    + Attributes (ErrorEnvelope)

## Session [/auth/session]

### Get Session [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (PortalSession)

+ Response 401 (application/json)
    + Attributes (ErrorEnvelope)

## Logout [/auth/logout]

### Logout [POST]

+ Response 204

# Data Structures

## ErrorEnvelope (object)
+ error: unauthorized (string, required)
+ message: Missing API key. (string, required)
+ requestId: `3f1da40a` (string, required)

## Snapshot (object)
+ id: `01HZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ` (string, required)
+ status: ready (string, required)
+ sourceUpdatedAt: `2026-03-22T12:34:20Z` (string, required)
+ importedAt: `2026-03-22T18:02:11Z` (string, required)
+ datasetVersion: `2026-03-22` (string, required)

## PlatformStats (object)
+ snapshotCount: 12 (number, required)
+ titleCount: 10900000 (number, required)
+ ratingCount: 1600000 (number, required)
+ episodeCount: 6200000 (number, required)
+ nameCount: 14000000 (number, required)

## Resolution (object)
+ input: Paradise (string, required)
+ resolvedTconst: tt27444205 (string, required)
+ matchReason: exact_primary_title_with_filters (string, required)
+ appliedFilters (object)
    + titleType: tvSeries (string)
    + year: 2025 (number)
+ alternatives (array[TitleSummary], optional)

## TitleSummary (object)
+ tconst: tt27444205 (string, required)
+ titleType: tvSeries (string, required)
+ primaryTitle: Paradise (string, required)
+ originalTitle: Paradise (string, required)
+ isAdult: false (boolean, required)
+ startYear: 2025 (number, optional)
+ endYear: null (number, nullable)
+ runtimeMinutes: null (number, nullable)
+ genres (array[string], required)
    + Action
    + Drama
    + Thriller
+ rating (RatingSummary, optional)

## RatingSummary (object)
+ averageRating: 7.8 (number, required)
+ numVotes: 1500 (number, required)

## TitleDetail (object)
+ title (TitleSummary, required)
+ rating (RatingSummary, optional)
+ episodeInfo (EpisodeInfo, optional)
+ crew (CrewMemberSummary, optional)
+ principals (array[PrincipalCredit], optional)

## Rating (object)
+ tconst: tt32459853 (string, required)
+ averageRating: 7.8 (number, required)
+ numVotes: 1500 (number, required)

## EpisodeInfo (object)
+ parentTconst: tt27444205 (string, required)
+ seasonNumber: 1 (number, optional)
+ episodeNumber: 2 (number, optional)

## EpisodeRating (object)
+ tconst: tt32459853 (string, required)
+ seasonNumber: 1 (number, optional)
+ episodeNumber: 2 (number, optional)
+ averageRating: 7.8 (number, required)
+ numVotes: 1500 (number, required)

## EpisodeDetail (object)
+ episode (TitleSummary, required)
+ episodeInfo (EpisodeInfo, required)
+ rating (RatingSummary, optional)

## SeriesEpisodeRatingsResponse (object)
+ series (TitleSummary, required)
+ resolution (Resolution, optional)
+ episodes (array[EpisodeRating], required)

## SeriesEpisodesResponse (object)
+ series (TitleSummary, required)
+ episodes (array[EpisodeDetail], required)

## PrincipalCredit (object)
+ ordering: 1 (number, required)
+ nconst: nm1250791 (string, required)
+ category: actor (string, required)
+ job: null (string, nullable)
+ characters (array[string], optional)
    + Xavier Collins
+ name (NameSummary, optional)

## CrewCredit (object)
+ role: director (string, required)
+ nconst: nm0275629 (string, required)
+ name (NameSummary, optional)

## CrewMemberSummary (object)
+ directors (array[CrewCredit], required)
+ writers (array[CrewCredit], required)

## CreditsResponse (object)
+ title (TitleSummary, required)
+ crew (CrewMemberSummary, required)
+ principals (array[PrincipalCredit], required)

## PrincipalsResponse (object)
+ title (TitleSummary, required)
+ principals (array[PrincipalCredit], required)

## CrewResponse (object)
+ title (TitleSummary, required)
+ crew (CrewMemberSummary, required)

## AlternateTitle (object)
+ title: Paradies (string, required)
+ region: DE (string, optional)
+ language: de (string, optional)
+ types (array[string], optional)
+ attributes (array[string], optional)
+ isOriginalTitle: false (boolean, required)

## AkasResponse (object)
+ title (TitleSummary, required)
+ akas (array[AlternateTitle], required)

## AkaSearchHit (object)
+ title (AlternateTitle, required)
+ matchedTconst: tt27444205 (string, required)
+ matchedPrimaryTitle: Paradise (string, required)

## AkaSearchResponse (object)
+ results (array[AkaSearchHit], required)

## NameSummary (object)
+ nconst: nm1250791 (string, required)
+ primaryName: Sterling K. Brown (string, required)
+ birthYear: 1976 (number, optional)
+ deathYear: null (number, nullable)
+ primaryProfession (array[string], optional)

## NameDetail (object)
+ name (NameSummary, required)
+ knownForTitles (array[string], required)
    + tt27444205
    + tt1442437

## NameTitleCredit (object)
+ tconst: tt27444205 (string, required)
+ category: actor (string, required)
+ job: null (string, nullable)
+ ordering: 1 (number, required)
+ title (TitleSummary, optional)

## NameSearchResponse (object)
+ results (array[NameSummary], required)

## NameTitlesResponse (object)
+ name (NameSummary, required)
+ titles (array[NameTitleCredit], required)

## ResolvedTitleResponse (object)
+ resolution (Resolution, required)
+ title (TitleDetail, required)

## TitleSearchResponse (object)
+ results (array[TitleSummary], required)

## BulkLookupRequest (object)
+ identifiers (array[string], required)
    + tt27444205
    + tt32459853

## BulkResolveItem (object)
+ title: Paradise (string, required)
+ titleType: tvSeries (string, optional)
+ year: 2025 (number, optional)

## BulkResolveRequest (object)
+ items (array[BulkResolveItem], required)

## BulkTitleResponse (object)
+ results (array[TitleDetail], required)
+ missing (array[string], required)

## BulkResolvedTitleResponse (object)
+ results (array[ResolvedTitleResponse], required)

## BulkRatingsResponse (object)
+ results (array[Rating], required)
+ missing (array[string], required)

## BulkEpisodeResponse (object)
+ results (array[EpisodeDetail], required)
+ missing (array[string], required)

## BulkSeriesEpisodeRatingsResponse (object)
+ results (array[SeriesEpisodeRatingsResponse], required)
+ missing (array[string], required)

## BulkNamesRequest (object)
+ identifiers (array[string], required)
    + nm1250791
    + nm0629855

## BulkNamesResponse (object)
+ results (array[NameDetail], required)
+ missing (array[string], required)

## BulkJobCreateRequest (object)
+ operation: titles.bulk.get (string, required)
+ payload (object, required)

## BulkJob (object)
+ id: `01HZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ` (string, required)
+ status: queued (string, required)
+ operation: titles.bulk.get (string, required)
+ createdAt: `2026-03-23T18:02:11Z` (string, required)
+ updatedAt: `2026-03-23T18:02:11Z` (string, required)
+ expiresAt: `2026-03-30T18:02:11Z` (string, required)
+ resultUrl: /v1/bulk/jobs/01HZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ/result (string, optional)

## BulkJobResultEnvelope (object)
+ job (BulkJob, required)
+ result (object, required)

## PortalUser (object)
+ id: `01HUSERZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ` (string, required)
+ email: engineer@nexioapp.org (string, required)
+ displayName: Nexio Engineer (string, optional)
+ avatarUrl: `https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/...` (string, optional)

## PortalSession (object)
+ authenticated: true (boolean, required)
+ user (PortalUser, required)

